info.author: Philippe Dalet
info.description:
HP3478A is an HP-Agilent multimeter 5.5 digit with GPIB.
This module can be used with the 82357A USB-GPIB which runs
only on windows (XP pro,W2K,Me,W98).

- Connect 82357A on USB port
- Install agilent driver (see CDROM IO libraries for instrument control
  Revision: L.02.00)
- Install 82357A  python package.
- Install this python package HP3478A.
